Package: python-gpsoauth
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}
Description: Google Play Services OAuth
 gpsoauth allows python code to use the "master token" flow
 described at:
 http://sbktech.blogspot.com/2014/01/inside-android-play-services-magic.html.
 .
 This can be useful when writing code that poses as a Google app,
 like 'gmusicapi' does.
 .
 This package contains the gpsoauth Python module.
